    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/2db0133d0c2adab751d8845af916fbb1.webp?t=1729463656\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Melt them All </strong>is action rogue-lite where you must <strong>survive </strong>as long as possible to maximizing your <strong>energy production </strong>in the process.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fight and survive</strong> against hordes of enemies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/f233f1829b8beb1d91ec1637480c60ee.poster.avif?t=1729463656\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/f233f1829b8beb1d91ec1637480c60ee.webm?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/f233f1829b8beb1d91ec1637480c60ee.mp4?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Create gigantic production chains </strong>to speed up the mining of ore.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/e647a42a9954620a29066fe7234d06cd.poster.avif?t=1729463656\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/e647a42a9954620a29066fe7234d06cd.webm?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/e647a42a9954620a29066fe7234d06cd.mp4?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find the best arrangement of buildings</strong> to survive as long as possible</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/66926a78f5810f7bd6fbed0bf5e52474.poster.avif?t=1729463656\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/66926a78f5810f7bd6fbed0bf5e52474.webm?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/66926a78f5810f7bd6fbed0bf5e52474.mp4?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Remote control your mining cart</strong> to collect ore</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/1efc68f3c25e5133f1ea5a9dc0958180.poster.avif?t=1729463656\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/1efc68f3c25e5133f1ea5a9dc0958180.webm?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/1efc68f3c25e5133f1ea5a9dc0958180.mp4?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade buildings and weapons during a playthrough</strong> to kill, mine and produce even more effectively.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/91f5270b6665ee782721e3ceea43db5b.poster.avif?t=1729463656\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/91f5270b6665ee782721e3ceea43db5b.webm?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/91f5270b6665ee782721e3ceea43db5b.mp4?t=1729463656\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Briefing from <strong>Sergeant</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/4735d15fedd0bcf5a235d13a17052ce7.apng?t=1729463656\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3252500/extras/4735d15fedd0bcf5a235d13a17052ce7.poster.avif?t=1729463656\" class=\"bb_img\" width=384 height=480 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Alright, you slimy space worms! Listen up! I ain't here to hold your hand through the cosmos! You've been drafted into the ranks of the best intergalactic mining troop, a <strong>spaceman</strong>. Your sorry selves have been <strong>shipped off to some godforsaken planet to extract resources.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, here's the deal: seems like the only thing worth a darn on this rock is the local critters. Yeah, you heard me right! Those squirming, scuttling creatures are the key . <strong>Your job? Round 'em up and toss 'em into the melting pot to keeping the lights on for our families back home.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No time for morals, this is survival! Get out there and get it done, because in space, it's them or us. Move out, spaceman!&quot; </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Missing Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The following is a list of things I would like to add if there is intrest. Just open a discussion in the community hub.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meta progression</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Controller support</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Settings to control screenshake</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
